title: The Steve Wilkos Show I Was Tortured As A Child

I WAS TORTURED AS A CHILD:
--------------------------



A life in captivity... As a young child, Mary claims her parents subjected her to extreme levels of physical and sexual abuse. To this day, she has been unable to live a normal life, suffering from frequent panic attacks, and never truly feeling she can trust someone.
